# Metric units

- Prefer **metric** in recipe text and structured amounts: g, kg, ml, L, °C.
- Use consistent abbreviations; avoid imperial-only strings unless you intentionally add dual labels.
- When cleaning imported data, normalize toward metric when the source allows.
